        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Safer Heat Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Consumer Product Safety Commission to establish safety standards for portable heating devices, including a requirement that a device shuts off at a threshold determined hazardous by the commission. The commission is authorized to enforce these standards.</p>]]>
        </text>
